<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Denied</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5e6e0 0%, #e8d5cd 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 520px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 4px solid #d67861;
        }

        .icon-circle {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d67861 0%, #c96855 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(214, 120, 97, 0.3);
            position: relative;
        }

        .icon-circle::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(214, 120, 97, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
        }

        .icon-circle svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            stroke: white;
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 2.5;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #5a3a31;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .message {
            color: #7d6660;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #fef5f3;
            border-left: 4px solid #d67861;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: #d67861;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .info-box p {
            color: #7d6660;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .info-box p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .error-code {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(214, 120, 97, 0.1);
            color: #d67861;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d67861 0%, #c96855 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(214, 120, 97, 0.3);
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(214, 120, 97, 0.4);
        }

        .button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon-circle">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
                <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"></line>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>Can't Access This Route</h1>

        <p class="message">
            You don't have permission to access this page. This area is restricted to specific user roles.
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Why am I seeing this?</h3>
            <p>You're trying to access a route that doesn't match your account type. For example:</p>
            <p>
                • Students cannot access professor/admin routes<br>
                • Professors cannot access student-specific routes
            </p>
            <p>Please navigate to your appropriate dashboard or contact support if you believe this is an error.</p>
            <span class="error-code">ERROR 403: FORBIDDEN</span>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
            <button class="button" onclick="goBack()">Go to Dashboard</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>
    function goBack(){
        window.history.back()
    }
</script>
</html>
